title: Brain Eaters From Outer Space
quote: Earth woman, I will eat your brains!
altHero: a woman screams as an alien shadow approaches her
alt1: the woman opens a window as a hand reaches for her
alt2: the woman hides as two hands lower pieces of bread around her head
alt3: the woman sees the brain eater, a green human-like alien
alt4: the brain eater opens wide to take a bite of the woman’s head, now shaved with a dotted line marked on it
